#CHIP K054539
#CLOCK 16000000

; K054539 (Konami Enhanced PCM) Basic Test
;
; The K054539 is an enhanced version of the Konami PCM chip.
; It has 8 channels of 16-bit PCM playback with additional features.
;
; Tests:
; - All 8 channels with basic sample playback
; - Volume control
; - Stereo panning

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1-4: Left stereo
c4 .

; Channel 5-8: Right stereo
d4 .

r4

; All 8 channels together
c4 & d4 & e4 & f4 & g4 & a4 & b4 & c5 .

r4

; Arpeggio across all channels
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 . g4 . a4 .

r2

#END
